{"tid":2337923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區議員林兆彬： 「香港加油」新年燈飾　遭民政署以「影響社會和諧」為由拒批","createTime":"2020-12-23T15:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T08:10:05.000Z","uid":22556,"like":19,"dislike":280,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"bd617c1a8383ad0634320b3ba6b6dd4967538dce","tid":2337923,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"油尖旺區議會早前討論節日燈飾設計，該區區議員林兆彬於會上提出「香港加油」四字的建議，提議獲節日慶典活動籌委會通過；但他稱昨日收到民政署回覆，署方「為免引起誤會及影響社會和諧」為由，拒絕採用有關字眼，並以「恭賀新禧」代替。林兆彬形容事件荒謬，「『香港加油』四隻字好中性，咁樣都 ban 」，批評署方是進一步削弱區議員權力。<br />\n<br />\n林兆彬向《立場新聞》透露，他早於今年 9 月向該區節日慶典活動籌委會提議，以「連登豬」為節日燈飾設計，當時籌委會亦通過有關提議，但最終民政署以「有政治含意、影響社會和諧」為由拒絕採用；並指若區議會堅持設計不會為項目招標，最終社區撥款工作小組被迫更改設計。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%80%A1%E8%A8%AD-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%B9-%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%87%88%E9%A3%BE-%E9%81%AD%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BB%A5-%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%A7-%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E6%8B%92%E6%89%B9/?fbclid=IwAR3WDcpqbcxcXdh5EeFbIZgsBkuxL6c0mEGCLBLGmyGfDB3Rp1_jl7TniHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2580%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%25B2%25B9-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2587%2588%25E9%25A3%25BE-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25AB%25A7-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%2589%25B9%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3WDcpqbcxcXdh5EeFbIZgsBkuxL6c0mEGCLBLGmyGfDB3Rp1_jl7TniHo&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp0B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=39e8829c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2580%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AD-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%25B2%25B9-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%